orge Bush</span><hr size=1> As far as labor unions go, I dont consider them socialist, I just consider them humane.  It turns out employers find themsleves more successful when they have happy motivated employees that aren't being worked like drones.  Its just that simple, dont go crediting socialism for the success of labor unions. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uaskander.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Askander</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I can beat up Bruin, np</span><br>  Posts: 1156<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 12:31:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6253.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Letter to George Bush</span><hr size=1> MO: Socialism fails and capitalism succeeds because humans are greedy by nature. <p><SELECT><OPTION SELECTED>Askander Bladebane (37) -  Cleric of Bruins Maruaders<OPTION>Balamorm SolRendyr (24) - Fuzzy Warrior of Bruins Marauders (Now with new and improved fuzziness)<OPTION>Althain Truetone (20) - Way-too-happy Bard of Sovereign Storm<OPTION>Askander Bladebane(not very creative am I?) - Sneaky Thane of Entwined Faith, Percival<OPTION>Email - - - joshlafaber@tigeraircraft.com</SELECT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ucowardlymonk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cowardly Monk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Black Reaver</span><br>  Posts: 1137<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 12:33:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6253.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Letter to George Bush</span><hr size=1> Labor Unions are 