erage person of exceptional intelligence/ability is not properly rewarded for their job.<br><br>The middle class will never perform as they should because they will constantly have their noses rubbed in the fact that they are considered equal to the lazy, shiftless and stupid.<br><br>And in a society where everyone is considered equal the only motivation will be self-motivation.  And that is in VERY short supply within the human race. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showMessageRange?topicID=6253.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showMessageRange?topicID=6253.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showMessageRange?topicID=6253.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showMessageRange?topicID=6253.topic&start=81&stop=96>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showPrevMessage?topicID=6253.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showNextMessage?topicID=6253.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6253.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.emailToFriend?topicID=6253.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.threadControl?topicID=6253.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</